items.title: Former Sequoia partner’s new startup uses AI to negotiate your calendar for you
items.description: Blockit, an AI agent that communicates directly with other calendars, has raised $5 million in seed funding led by Sequoia.

items.title: Vimeo starts layoffs after acquisition by Bending Spoons
